# Financial Risk Management Capital Balancing Item Liability Component Amount

## identifier
de4973

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of the liability component less the value of effective borrowings and tax liabilities.

The Liability Component is determined as the realistic value of liabilities of the General Fund plus, in the case of a friendly society, the reserve in respect of servicing expenses and investment-linked business.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.ManagementCapital.BalancingItemLiabilityComponent.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
